Installation
==============================

ucesb depends on flex, bison, ncurses, perl and optionally on PAW and ROOT.
Depending on your platform the installation instructions for these vary.

This document with detail how to install the required depencies.

Debain based (Ubuntu/Mint/...)
------------------------------
The requirements can be fullfilled by executing

apt-get install bison flex libncurses5-dev build-essentials


Red-hat based (Scientific linux/Cern CentOS7/SUSE)
------------------------------
The requirements can be fullfilled by executing

yum install bison flex ncurses-devel make perl-Digest-MD5


MacOS
------------------------------
The requirements can be fullfilled with homebrew

homebrew install bison flex ncurses

